# bubbleShoot-Game


In Angular with service and game setter</br>
How to play this game: </br>
1. Open Index.html in the browser</br>
2. Set grid size, game size, game time limit, number of chances to win the game</br>
3. Save game rules</br>
4. Click on start button to play the game</br>
5. You have to uncolour the colored circles by simple clicking on the colored circles within the time limit set</br>
6. If you are unable to complete the game within the setted time, you will get more chances based on the number of chances saved</br>
7. Once all chnces finished and still there are colord circles on the board you loose the game else you win </br>
